### health
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### create worker
POST http://localhost:5000/v1/workers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Ion Ionescu",
  "department": "Construction",
  "role": "Electrician"
}

### assign NFC to worker (replace :id)
POST http://localhost:5000/v1/workers/1/nfc
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uid_hex": "04FFEEDDCC11",
  "deactivate_others": true
}

### reader heartbeat (paste your device key from console)
POST http://localhost:5000/v1/readers/heartbeat
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_DEVICE_KEY

### simulate scan (paste the same device key)
POST http://localhost:5000/v1/scans
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_DEVICE_KEY
Content-Type: application/json

{ "uid_hex": "04FFEEDDCC11" }

### simulate checkout (run again)
POST http://localhost:5000/v1/scans
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_DEVICE_KEY
Content-Type: application/json

{ "uid_hex": "04FFEEDDCC11" }

### list sessions for worker 1
GET http://localhost:5000/v1/workers/1/sessions

### hours report (all workers, last 90 days)
GET http://localhost:5000/v1/reports/hours?from=2025-01-01&to=2025-12-31

### hours report (construction only)
GET http://localhost:5000/v1/reports/hours?from=2025-01-01&to=2025-12-31&location_type=construction
